snippet.title: Atari Lynx Longplay [52] Jimmy Connors Tennis
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Challenge various tennis players until you get the chance to challenge Jimmy Connors himself. Sometimes the tennis players challenges you, which happened only once during this longplay, but certainly prolonged this boring game for a bit more. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
